- if @no_apps_installed
  = haml :install_app
- else
  %h3
    - if @streaks.empty?
      You haven't logged any streaks yet.
      %br
      %h4
        %br
        Keep on surfing, and come back later :-)
    - else
      Streaks

  - for streak in @streaks
    = streak
%h4
  Your personalized data will appear on this page once you've set up the extension and logged your first streak.
